CBRE, as the exclusive sales agent, are pleased to present to market 6 Lansdowne Street, Merrylands for sale by Expressions of Interest. The property is a single storey, four-bedroom cottage style dwelling set on a generous land holding of 767 square metres*, with a 20m* frontage to Lansdowne Street. The property presents itself as a prime raw development site suitable for multiple uses including boarding houses, centre based childcare facilities, commercial premises and shop top housing (STCA).  

6 Lansdowne Street, Merrylands benefits from the following key attributes:

•Terrific land holding
•Total land area: 767sqm*
•Accessibility to major business hubs via Great Western Highway and the M4 Motorway
•B4 Mixed Use Zoning, prime for childcare, education, shop top housing, seniors housing and medical development (STCA)
•Ideally located in an ever-growing region and in proximity to fantastic services and amenities including Stockland Merrylands, ALDI Guildford, Westfield Parramatta, as well as bus and train services.  
•Highly favourable planning controls including an FSR of 2:1, and HOB of 31 metres

6 Lansdowne Street, Merrylands will be sold via an expressions of interest campaign, closing on Tuesday 27 July 2021 at 2:00pm.
